videos.description: Josh Perkins passes the ball ahead to Rui Hachimura, who glides to the bucket for a thunderous slam.
videos.headline: Hachimura rises up for monster dunk

videos.description: Rui Hachimura goes to the spin move to get to the basket for a layup off the glass.
videos.headline: Hachimura spins by defender for layup

videos.description: With time running out and the game tied, Rui Hachimura knocks down a midrange jumper with 0.6 seconds left and Gonzaga would hold on to win.
videos.headline: Hachimura drains game-winning jumper
